data.description: Sprawling family home with a bonus barn-style workshop in Rose Hill! Enjoy living in this spacious split-level home with 3 beds, 2.5 baths, a 2-car attached garage and an additional barn-style workshop/garage with covered carport. This home is the perfect combination of an interior decorator and prepper’s dream! Beautiful layout provides efficient distribution of rooms with a combined function for family safety. The walls of the home are 12” thick concrete with a storm shelter in the middle of the home. There are hookups available for a Generac and for your RV. The wood-burning fireplace at the lower level provides a wonderful and useful aesthetic in the family room downstairs. Three large bedrooms have access to 2 large full baths and a half bath, with a bonus attic area you can convert into additional sleeping quarters. All mounted TVs remain with the home and are wired for cable. Live within walking distance to schools in a friendly neighborhood. This is a well-loved home that is ready for a new beginning with a new family! Come and see this home today. Call to schedule a private showing.
